<rss xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" version="2.0"><channel><title>Guava-Cache - 标签 - 咔咔不太卡的博客</title><link>https://ksmaple.github.io/tags/guava-cache/</link><description>Guava-Cache - 标签 - 咔咔不太卡的博客</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Thu, 30 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://ksmaple.github.io/tags/guava-cache/" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>本地缓存方案</title><link>https://ksmaple.github.io/posts/%E8%BF%9B%E9%98%B6%E5%B1%82/%E7%BC%93%E5%AD%98%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF/%E6%9C%AC%E5%9C%B0%E7%BC%93%E5%AD%98/</link><pubDate>Thu, 30 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>咔咔</author><guid>https://ksmaple.github.io/posts/%E8%BF%9B%E9%98%B6%E5%B1%82/%E7%BC%93%E5%AD%98%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF/%E6%9C%AC%E5%9C%B0%E7%BC%93%E5%AD%98/</guid><description><![CDATA[<h1 id="本地缓存方案">本地缓存方案</h1>
<blockquote>
<p><strong>核心结论</strong>：本地缓存通过避免网络IO和序列化开销提供纳秒级访问速度，Caffeine凭借W-TinyLFU算法和异步加载机制成为Java本地缓存的首选，与Redis配合使用形成多级缓存架构。</p>
</blockquote>
<hr>
<h2 id="本地缓存通过避免网络开销提供极致性能caffeine基于w-tinylfu算法在命中率上领先与redis配合形成多级缓存">本地缓存通过避免网络开销提供极致性能，Caffeine基于W-TinyLFU算法在命中率上领先，与Redis配合形成多级缓存</h2>
<h3 id="caffeine高性能本地缓存">Caffeine：高性能本地缓存</h3>
<div class="code-block code-line-numbers open" style="counter-reset: code-block 0">
    <div class="code-header language-java">
        <span class="code-title"><i class="arrow fas fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="ellipses"><i class="fas fa-ellipsis-h" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="copy" title="复制到剪贴板"><i class="far fa-copy" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-java" data-lang="java"><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1">// Caffeine基本用法</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">LoadingCache</span><span class="o">&lt;</span><span class="n">String</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">User</span><span class="o">&gt;</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">userCache</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">Caffeine</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="na">newBuilder</span><span class="p">()</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">    </span><span class="p">.</span><span class="na">maximumSize</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">10000</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w">                          </span><span class="c1">// 最大条目数</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">    </span><span class="p">.</span><span class="na">expireAfterWrite</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">10</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">TimeUnit</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="na">MINUTES</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w">      </span><span class="c1">// 写入后10分钟过期</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">    </span><span class="p">.</span><span class="na">refreshAfterWrite</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">1</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">TimeUnit</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="na">MINUTES</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w">      </span><span class="c1">// 1分钟后异步刷新</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">    </span><span class="p">.</span><span class="na">recordStats</span><span class="p">()</span><span class="w">                                </span><span class="c1">// 开启统计</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">    </span><span class="p">.</span><span class="na">build</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">key</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">loadUserFromDB</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">key</span><span class="p">));</span><span class="w">          </span><span class="c1">// 自动加载</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">User</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">user</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">userCache</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="na">get</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s">&#34;user:1001&#34;</span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w">  </span><span class="o">//</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">存在则返回</span><span class="err">，</span><span class="n">不存在则自动加载</span></span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<p><strong>Caffeine核心特性</strong>：</p>
<table>
  <thead>
      <tr>
          <th>特性</th>
          <th>说明</th>
      </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
      <tr>
          <td>W-TinyLFU淘汰策略</td>
          <td>比LRU更高的命中率，适应访问频率变化</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>异步加载</td>
          <td>缓存未命中时异步加载，不阻塞主线程</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>自动刷新</td>
          <td>后台线程异步刷新过期缓存</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>弱引用支持</td>
          <td>允许Key/Value被GC回收</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>事件监听</td>
          <td>移除、过期事件回调</td>
      </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>
<p><strong>缓存淘汰策略对比</strong>：</p>
<table>
  <thead>
      <tr>
          <th>策略</th>
          <th>原理</th>
          <th>特点</th>
      </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
      <tr>
          <td>LRU</td>
          <td>最近最少使用</td>
          <td>实现简单，但对突发流量敏感</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>LFU</td>
          <td>最少使用频率</td>
          <td>历史频率高但不再访问的数据难以淘汰</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>W-TinyLFU</td>
          <td>频率+时间窗口</td>
          <td>兼顾历史频率和近期访问，自适应</td>
      </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>
