<h3 id="多级缓存架构">多级缓存架构</h3>
<div class="code-block code-line-numbers open" style="counter-reset: code-block 0">
    <div class="code-header language-">
        <span class="code-title"><i class="arrow fas fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="ellipses"><i class="fas fa-ellipsis-h" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="copy" title="复制到剪贴板"><i class="far fa-copy" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback"><span class="line"><span class="cl">请求 → L1本地缓存（Caffeine）→ hit → 返回（~纳秒级）
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">              ↓ miss
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">        L2分布式缓存（Redis）→ hit → 写L1 → 返回（~微秒级）
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">              ↓ miss
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">        DB → 写L2 → 写L1 → 返回（~毫秒级）
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">一致性保障：
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  - 写操作：先写DB，删Redis，广播通知各节点删本地缓存
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  - 本地缓存TTL设置短于Redis（如Redis 10分钟，本地2分钟）</span></span></code></pre></div></div>
